    off:["Ruled a single-vehicle, traffic-related fatal crash and fire by the Alabama Law Enforcement Agency; no published ruling of homicide, abduction, or third-party action as of this entry. The 'kidnapping' and similar framings in tabloid coverage are not official findings, treat them as speculation. FBI interest in 2025-26 'scientist cluster' reporting, referenced by Fox and others, is about pattern review across many cases, not a published determination that this crash was connected to others. The Livelsberger manifesto's technical claims (gravitic propulsion) were not vetted for truth by the FBI, only the email's origin was confirmed, per LVMPD 2025 statements."],
